unisDot11ACStaUserAuthRespCntCM OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX      Counter32
    MAX-ACCESS  read-only
    STATUS      current
    DESCRIPTION
        "Represents the total number of user authenticate response with this AC."
    ::= { unisDot11ACStaUserSecAuthStatis 7 }

